descriptionNullable:
Sentiment analysis on natural language sentences can increase the accuracy of market prediction because financial markets are influenced by investor sentiments. Many investors also base their decisions on information taken from newspapers or on their instincts.

in this dataset you can find 100K tweets containing NVIDIA in 2023 and 2022.

For more information please check out the notebook in the code.
